Insider Activity


Individual




Katie J. Bayne



Ms. Katie J. Bayne is Independent Director at Ascena Retail Group, Inc. and Senior Vice President-Global Sparkling Brands at The Coca-Cola Co. She is on the Board of Directors at Ascena Retail Group, Inc., The Atlanta Womens Foundation, Inc., American Film Institute, Inc., and The Lovett School.
Ms. Bayne was previously employed as a Principal by Coca Cola South Pacific Pty Ltd. and President-Brands by Coca-Cola North America. She also served on the board at ANN, Inc. and Beazer Homes USA, Inc.
She received her undergraduate degree from Duke University and an MBA from The Fuqua School of Business.



